net.enilink.komma.model

Interface IObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IModelAware, IReference, IReferenceable, IResource, IValue, Resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectSupport

    public interface IObject
extends IEntity, IResource, IModelAware
    The base interface of a bean that is contained within an IModel.

    An IObject is an entity that additionally implements the IModelAware interface to access the associated model via IModelAware.getModel().

    An IObject instance also implements the IResource interface that allows to access RDF types and properties of the resource by using general object-oriented methods (comparable to Java reflection).
